data.description: Wonderful Waters Edge interior lot with lake views from the front and back (even better in the winter) just hit the market on Lake Keowee!! This spacious Three story home features four bedrooms, three bathrooms, as well as a media room, bunk room, sitting room and two living rooms in over 3700 sq ft of living space. The entire third floor is the owner’s suite with a double shower, jetted tub, large walk-in closet, private sitting room, and balcony to enjoy the lake views after a day on the water. This home is ideal for large gatherings as a 2nd home or your primary residence. The kitchen is ready for entertaining and includes double ovens and a built-in cooktop and is located on the second floor to maximize natural light and opens to the back deck, dining room and 2nd living room. Enter the home through the beautiful double wooden doors into your 1st living room with vaulted ceilings up to the open 2nd floor living room. Located in the quiet gated neighborhood of Waters Edge, the community has a private boat ramp, dock, and community area. Three boat slips also available to purchase for all your lake boating needs! Call today to schedule your showing!
